OL,5,CBirmingham
OL,7,FThis is the moment a rapist was
OL,8,Farrested by police after he subjected
OL,9,Ftwo women to a horrific ordeal.
OL,11,FTroy Tomlin wore a mask when he met
OL,12,Fwith a woman at a flat near Birmingham
OL,13,Fcity centre.
OL,15,FHe had arranged to meet on an escort
OL,16,Fwebsite and was wearing a face
OL,17,Fcovering when he arrived in June last
OL,18,Fyear.
