OL,7,FThe 27-year-old told the woman that
OL,8,Fthis was because he had come from work
OL,9,Fand he wanted to protect his identity.
OL,11,FBut Tomlin, of Portland Road,
OL,12,FBirmingham, soon pulled out a gun and
OL,13,Fdemanded to know where the woman's
OL,14,Fmoney was.
OL,16,FShe handed him some cash before Tomlin
OL,17,Fentered another room where a second
OL,18,Fwoman was.
