OL,7,FThis woman also handed over some cash,
OL,8,Fbut Tomlin was not finished with the
OL,9,Fhorrific ordeal and he went on to rape
OL,10,Fboth women.
OL,12,FAt one point, he held a gun to one of
OL,13,Fhis victim's heads and demanded to see
OL,14,Ftheir ID.
OL,16,FHe threatened to go to their homes and
OL,17,Fkill them if either of the women went
OL,18,Fto the police.
