OL,7,FBoth women bravely managed to flee the
OL,8,Fproperty and raise the alarm before
OL,9,FTomlin fled the scene.
OL,11,FPolice managed to trace him using
OL,12,Fmobile data and he was arrested two
OL,13,Fdays later when he failed to stop in a
OL,14,Fwhite Volvo.
OL,16,FTomlin was found guilty of four rapes,
OL,17,Ftwo counts of possession of an
OL,18,Fimitation firearm with intent to cause
OL,19,Ffear of violence, robbery, possession
OL,20,Fof a knife and possession of cannabis.
