OL,7,FHe was jailed for life with a minimum
OL,8,Fof 17 years at Birmingham Crown Court
OL,9,Fon Monday, February 10.
OL,11,FDet Insp Matt Owen, from the West
OL,12,FMidlands Police Public Protection
OL,13,FUnit, said: "This was an horrific and
OL,14,Fsustained attack on two women, causing
OL,15,Fboth real fear and a significant and
OL,16,Flasting impact.
OL,18,F"Tomlin tried to lie his way out of
OL,19,Fthis by suggesting that the sex had
OL,20,Fbeen consensual, but the jury was able
OL,21,Fto see through that."
